Hey Mo how's it going?
Just wondering what sort of questions you would like me to ask RE starting your own business and things?

Just letting you know a quick update, since last talking to you I've been on three different projects, as is the way with advertising sometimes, and while primarily an animator, I have also worked as a co-script writer, co-art director, concept artist, storyboard artist and all other sorts of things, as is the nature of smaller businesses sometimes. Do you have any secondary skills you're looking to develop?
